metadata.name: Save-Our-Souls 4Mar2022
metadata.description:
A chance to personally support people.

All the bids (except gas expenses) go to support people hurt by war in Ukraine.

This bid goes to amazing artist Daria @Moonchild_14, who supports her friends and neighbors there.

- language-driven model
- freeform model
